00:02:24.437 --> 00:02:26.658
he claims that he has but one name

00:02:26.739 --> 00:02:28.960
I believe him when he says you know

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:30.900


00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:33.080
I want to always be known and remembered

00:02:33.140 --> 00:02:36.622
by I think he's telling us the truth

00:02:36.741 --> 00:02:38.443
and when he says that his name is

00:02:38.483 --> 00:02:40.883
based upon the verb Hayah then I think

00:02:40.903 --> 00:02:42.465
